title: SEP Sesam License
agents: sep_sesam
catalog: app/backup
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 Monitors the SEP Sesam server license status and expiration date.

 The check reports OK when the license is valid, WARNING when expiration
 is within the configured warning threshold (default: 30 days), and
 CRITICAL when within the critical threshold (default: 15 days) or
 already expired.

 Additional information shown when available: license edition (e.g.
 Ultimate Volume), customer name, and volume usage (used TB vs. total
 TB of licensed FrontSide capacity).
